//www.uat-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-landen-van-de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-en-het-schengengebied\">member state of the European Economic Area</a>, for infringements of the environmental legislation concerning the use of the recognition.</li><li>in the 2 years that precede the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object was revoked due to infringement of the obligations associated with that recognition.</li></ul></li></ul><ul><li><strong>special recognition conditions:</strong><ul><li>have sound procedures to organise the examination in refrigeration of category I, II, III or IV and the update exam</li><li>organise a regulatory examination jury.</li></ul></li></ul><h2><strong>Validity period and obligations</strong></h2><p>The recognition is valid for an <strong>indefinite period</strong>. The training centre must meet the following obligations to retain recognition:</p><ul><li>organise <strong>quality </strong>examinations according to the instructions of the Government of Flanders</li><li>guarantee <strong>objectivity </strong>and <strong>independence</strong></li><li>have the <strong>necessary infrastructure </strong>in place to organise the examination</li><li><strong>award certificates </strong>and submit the examination file to the competent authorities</li><li>hold <strong>insurance </strong>for third-party liability, including professional liability, in connection with the use of the recognition</li></ul>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Om erkend te worden als opleidingscentrum voor koeltechnici moet het opleidingscentrum voldoen aan:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">algemene erkenningsvoorwaarden</a> die gelden voor alle erkenningen leefmilieu<ul><li>in de 3 jaar die de aanvraag van het Vlaamse erkenningsbewijs voorafgaan, heeft de aanvrager geen strafrechtelijke veroordeling opgelopen in een <a href=\"http